# Transp. Code
## Title 7
### Chapter 621. Gen. Provisions Relating to Vehicle Size & Weight
##### § 621.006 — Restricted Operation on Certain Holidays

The commission by rule may impose restrictions on the weight and size of vehicles to be operated on state highways on the following holidays only:

    (1) New Year’s Day;

    (2) Memorial Day;

    (3) Independence Day;

    (4) Labor Day;

    (5) Thanksgiving Day; and

    (6) Christmas Day.

*Acts 2011, 82nd Leg., R.S., Ch. 1345 (S.B.1420), Sec. 57, eff. September 1, 2011.*
